The paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep neural networks and adversarial training strategies suggests that the paper may also belong to the subcategories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of large-scale semantic supervision, which suggests that it may belong to the subcategory of graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the paper deals with image translation, which is a common task in multimedia (cs.MM).
